    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_3_883-927",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "883-927",
      "markText": "这本书于我，是一种虐读，全新的体验，折磨加享受，窒息式的快感；快感之后，是更持久的窒息。",
      "totalCount": 4284,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=883&rangeEnd=927",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=883&rangeEnd=927"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_3_1814-1894",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1814-1894",
      "markText": "我们以为自己生活在有希望的人间，哪知人间在魔鬼的陷阱里；我们以为自己长脚就有可能逃离，哪知道自己是粘在蛛网上的米蛾。人类的历史就是周而复始，永难逃脱魔鬼的怪圈。",
      "totalCount": 3728,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1814&rangeEnd=1894",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1814&rangeEnd=1894"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_4_481-499",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "481-499",
      "markText": "“那样的话，我不如用等待来错过它。”",
      "totalCount": 3552,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=481&rangeEnd=499",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=481&rangeEnd=499"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_5_10490-10556",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10490-10556",
      "markText": "他不仅不能，而且根本就不想离开这里，因为他在这里至少可以蜷缩在习以为常的风景的阴影里，但在外面，在村子外边，谁知道等待他的将是什么。",
      "totalCount": 2368,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10490&rangeEnd=10556",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10490&rangeEnd=10556"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_5_1257-1324",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1257-1324",
      "markText": "整个事件在岿然不动的永恒球体内，也只不过扮演一个小丑的角色，在混乱无序中诱唤魔鬼的良知，经营出一个优势地位，将疯癫伪造成生活的必需……",
      "totalCount": 2236,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1257&rangeEnd=1324",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1257&rangeEnd=1324"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_3_4610-4682",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4610-4682",
      "markText": "只要人类存在，大屠杀就会进行，因为大屠杀是一种人类文化，有墙的奥斯维辛虽被烧毁了，没有墙的奥斯维辛依旧存在，人们在战争的废墟上建立起和平的废墟。",
      "totalCount": 2028,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4610&rangeEnd=4682",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4610&rangeEnd=4682"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_3_711-762",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "711-762",
      "markText": "译稿发出去后，我跟责编抱怨：“简直就要憋死我了！现在我真想跺脚，喊叫，砸东西，摔书，再也不想看到它！”",
      "totalCount": 2016,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=711&rangeEnd=762",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=711&rangeEnd=762"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_5_7434-7455",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7434-7455",
      "markText": "我什么也不做，只看这该死的生活如何流逝……",
      "totalCount": 2016,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7434&rangeEnd=7455",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7434&rangeEnd=7455"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_12_19529-19622",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "19529-19622",
      "markText": "不知道这到底是怎么回事不知道现在是晨光破晓还是暮色降临 一切都无终无止没完没了他坐在那里不知道这究竟是怎么回事 外面没有发生任何改变 既不是早上也不是晚上只是继续不停地晨光破晓或暮色降临",
      "totalCount": 2002,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=19529&rangeEnd=19622",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=19529&rangeEnd=19622"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_5_13984-14059",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "13984-14059",
      "markText": "大雨滂沱，将施密特的咒骂和他激励的话语冲刷到一起，最后他只重复这一句话：“别垂头丧气，老伙计！你会看到，我们会有好命的，金子般的命！我们的黄金时代！”",
      "totalCount": 1904,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13984&rangeEnd=14059",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13984&rangeEnd=14059"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_3_3878-3903",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3878-3903",
      "markText": "希望是相对的，绝望是绝对的，一切都比绝望还更绝望。",
      "totalCount": 1872,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3878&rangeEnd=3903",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3878&rangeEnd=3903"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_5_5885-5960",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5885-5960",
      "markText": "在那里抠下一块硝石灰墙皮塞进嘴里细嚼慢品，为了能够通过搅乱气味、味道的正常秩序唤起自己的警觉，因为他相信，与令人绝望的永恒结局相比，死亡更是一种警告。",
      "totalCount": 1785,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5885&rangeEnd=5960",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5885&rangeEnd=5960"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24240795_9_17750-17807",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "17750-17807",
      "markText": "她梳了一下额前的头发，将大拇指塞进自己嘴里，闭上了眼睛。她没有理由感到不安。她清楚地知道，她的天使们已经在路上了。",
      "totalCount": 1752,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24240795&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=17750&rangeEnd=17807",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/657323107171e29b657dacd?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=17750&rangeEnd=17807"
    },
    {
